Debra Lafave, 25, will serve three years of house arrest and seven years of probation . She pleaded guilty Tuesday to two counts of lewd and lascivious battery . If convicted at trial in Hillsborough County, Florida, she could have faced up to 15 years in prison on each count.
 Nearly 18 months after her case sent the tabloids into a tizzy, Lafave, 25, pleaded guilty to two counts of lewd and lascivious battery as part of a plea agreement with prosecutors in Hillsborough and Marion County.
 The arrest is the second in as many years of a female Hillsborough County teacher accused of having sex with a teenage student.